            <thetext>The drag and drop eventhandler registers a &quot;mousedown&quot; listener at the document element to check if a drag session has to be started.
The window widget itself does stop all &quot;mousdown&quot;, &quot;mouseup&quot; and &quot;click&quot; events which breaks the drag and drop inside any window widget.

We need to find a solution to enable drag and drop inside window widgets.</thetext>
